column3: Lachhh is currently streaming some game development! Come over and say hi!
column4: Lachhh streamer i øjeblikket spil udvikling! Kom og sige hej!

column3: White Orbs will become Black Orbs
You will keep your medals, items and hell progress.
column4: Du vil holde dine medaljer, elementer og helvede fremskridt.

column3: That's a lot of skulls you've got here!
column4: Det er en masse kranier du har fået her!

column3: *In case you're wondering : no, this one is not a real InApp.*
column4: * Hvis du undrer dig: Nej, dette er ikke en ægte Køb i appen (InApp).*

column3: Wow, you really want to pay $750,000 and your soul for those diamonds?
column4: Wow, du vil virkelig betale $750.000 og din sjæl for disse diamanter?

column3: Ah ok, phew! I thought so!
column4: Ah ok, Pyha! troede jeg også!

column3: I mean, that's a ludicrous amount of money to pay for a virtual item, you still wanna buy that?
column4: Jeg mener, det er et latterligt beløb af penge til at betale for en virtuel vare, ønsker du stadig at købe det?

column3: You'll probably need to get another job, a loan, sell all of your belongings... Are you sure?
column4: Du vil sandsynligvis være nødt til at få et andet job, et lån, sælge alle dine ejendele... Er du sikker?

column3: That's kind of excessive don't you think? Don't you want to cancel now?
column4: Det er lidt overdrevet tror du ikke? ønsker du ikke at annullere nu?

column3: Okay I guess. I mean it's cool for us, that's a lot of money, but I just want to be sure you're ok with this.
column4: Okay tror jeg. Jeg mener det er cool for os, det er en masse penge, men jeg vil bare være sikker på, du er ok med dette.

column3: Oh okay... sorry. No need to be rude.
column4: Åh okay... undskyld. Ingen grund til at være uhøflig.

column3: I have to say, you are determined to get that pack.
column4: Jeg må sige, du er fast besluttet på at få denne pakke.

column3: Heh, determination, that reminds me of Undertale.
column4: Heh, beslutsomhed, det minder mig om Undertale.

column3: Have you played that game? It's super cool, you should try it.
column4: Har du spillet dette spil? Det er super cool, du skulle prøve det.

column3: ...and it's not even our game.  I mean Toby Fox is the guy who made it.  He's brilliant.
column4: ...og det er ikke engang vores spil.  Jeg mener, Toby Fox er den fyr der lavede det.  Han er genial.

column3: I think he got inspired by Mother 3...  or is it Earthbound?
column4: Jeg tror, han fik inspireret af Mother 3...  eller er det Earthbound?

column3: Hang on, is Earthbound and Mother 3 the same game? I never knew, I'm kinda confused by that.
column4: Hæng på, er Earthbound og Mother 3 det samme spil? det vidste jeg ikke, jeg er lidt forvirret over det.

column3: I think it's a lost in translation thing, kinda like Final Fantasy 6.... or 3. Whatever.
column4: Jeg tror det er en misforståelse i oversættelsen, ligesom Final Fantasy 6... eller 3. Uanset hvad.
Anyway jeg har aldrig spillet Earthbound.

column3: Yeah I know! It's lame right?
column4: Ja det ved jeg! Det er lidt lamt ikk?

column3: The thing is, I played it once when I was a kid, but I couldn't read English.
column4: Sagen er den, jeg spillede det engang, da jeg var barn, men jeg kunne ikke læse engelsk.

column3: So you know, it was kinda hard to play an RPG when you couldn't understand anything on the screen.
column4: Så du ved, det var lidt svært at spille en RPG, når du ikke kunne forstå noget af det på skærmen.

column3: I became good at English though!
column4: Så blev jeg god til engelsk selv!

column3: My mom was like 'Video games are useless!'
column4: Min mor var "like" «Video spil er ubrugelig!»

column3: But I showed her my English grades at school and she gave me a break.
column4: Men jeg så viste hende mine karakterer i engelsk, i skolen og hun gav mig en pause.

column3: I'm not afraid to say it, you know. I think it's cool to show her some love sometimes.
column4: Jeg er ikke bange for at sige det. Jeg synes, det er cool at vise hende noget kærlighed nogle gange.

column3: You know, she makes sure you don't miss anything in your life. Food... a house, toys.
column4: Du ved, hun sørger for, at du ikke går glip af noget i dit liv. Mad... et hus, legetøj.

column3: And we rarely get the chance to tell her that she is awesome.
column4: Og vi får sjældent chancen for at fortælle hende, at hun er fantastisk.

column3: You know what? That little chat kinda made me feel better.
column4: Ved du hvad? Denne lille snak fik mig til at få det bedre.

column3: It feels like you care about me.
column4: Det føles som om du holder af mig.

column3: Not only about those zombies, but about the developer behind it as well.
column4: Ikke kun zombierne, men om udvikleren bag det også.

column3: That's a very cool feeling, thank you. :)
column4: Det er en meget cool følelse, tak. :)

column3: As a token of gratitude, I'll give you 5 diamonds. Do you want them?
column4: Som et tegn på taknemmelighed, vil jeg give dig 5 diamanter. Vil du have dem?

column3: There! Thanks again for that little chat!
column4: Der! Tak igen for den lille snak!
Jeg er glad for du er her igen!

column3: I have no diamonds left for you though.
column4: Men Jeg har ingen diamanter, tilbage til dig.

column3: Well, that's not very true... I'm the dev, so I could give you infinite diamonds if I want.
column4: Nå, det er ikke helt sandt... Jeg er udvikler, så jeg kunne give dig uendelig diamanter, hvis jeg ønsker.

column3: But that wouldnt't be fair for the other players.
column4: Men det ville ikke være fair overfor de andre spillere.

column3: Now I feel bad, because I just told you that I could, but I won't.
column4: Nu føler jeg skam, fordi jeg lige fortalt dig, at jeg kunne, men, at jeg ikke vil.

column3: What kind of friend am I?
It's kind of like if you tell your wife, 'Hey I could give you chocolate, but I won't'.
column4: Det er lidt ligesom hvis du fortælle din kone, "Hey jeg kunne give dig chokolade, men jeg vil ikke".

column3: I should buy chocolates for my wife...
column4: Jeg burde købe chokolade til min kone...

column3: Oh well,\nThis one is on the house.
Ok ok! RELAX!\nNo need to panic!
column4: OK ok! Slap af!\nIngen grund til at gå i panik!
